description: This Digital Exclusive features OVER 100 PAGES of Dilton's wackiest creations! Dilton Doiley, Riverdale's resident nutty professor, has a new invention for you! Are you brave enough to see what is? Put on your labcoat and check out over 100 pages of Dilton's craziest scientific experiments. Whether it's a new robot, a time machine, or even a brain-switcher, if it's Dilton's invention, it's definitely doofy!
name: Dilton's Doofy Inventions

description: Best frenemies Betty & Veronica have been fighting over Archie for over 70 years! You've always known, however, that Betty's the one who ought to win that battle! She's always been crazy about Archie, and the two have always been a great pair. This 100-page digital exclusive collects some of Betty's best triumphs over Veronica. Join Riverdale's bubbliest blonde in the battle for Archie's heart!
name: Team Betty

description: Best frenemies Veronica & Betty have been fighting over Archie for over 70 years! You've always known, however, that Veronica's the one who should come out on top. She's refined, she's beautiful, and she can get Archie to drop everything for her! This 100-page digital exclusive collects some of Veronica's best victories over Betty. Join Riverdale's most vivacious vixen in the battle for Archie's heart!
name: Team Veronica

description: It's the ultimate battle for Archie's heart! Betty and Veronica, the best of frenemies, have been locked in a tug-of-war over Riverdale's favorite redhead for over 70 years. Will you root for Betty, the sweet and innocent girl-next-door, or for Veronica, the rich and sophisticated socialite? Will Archie finally be able to choose between them? Archie's girls go head-to-head in OVER 250 PAGES of winner-take-Arch stories!
name: Betty Vs. Veronica The Fight for Archie!

description: Monsters! Giant robots! Maniacs and masterminds! When evil rears its ugly head, you can be sure that the Explorers of the Unknown will be there to save the day! Join the team of heroes, who look a lot like our favorite Riverdale teens, as they battle a rogue cyclops, a giant crab monster, and the diabolical Doctor Gloom! Will these soldiers of fortune be able to triumph over the forces of evil? Find out in over 160 pages of action and adventure!
name: Archie's Explorers of the Unknown
